14 WHEREAS, pursuant to Section 308 of Title 75 of the Oklahoma
15 Statutes, the Oklahoma State Legislature shall adopt a separate
16 joint resolution to approve or disapprove major rules.
17 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES
18 AND THE SENATE OF THE 2ND SESSION OF THE 60TH OKLAHOMA LEGISLATURE:
19 SECTION 1. The Legislature hereby approves the following
20 proposed major rule changes submitted by the Office of Management
21 and Enterprise Services on or before February 1, 2026: OAC 260:75-
22 1-1; 260:75-1-2; 260:75-1-3; 260:75-1-4; 260:75-1-6; 260:75-1-7;
23 260:75-1-8; and 260:75-1-10.
24
